Description

Power Meets Precision Own the Game, Own the Room

  • MASSIVE 64 GB DDR 5 RAM 4 TB SSD - Effortlessly run multiple apps and store your entire digital universe with lightning-fast load times.
  • NEXT GEN NVIDIA GE FORCE RTX 4090 - Experience jaw-dropping graphics and real-time ray tracing that puts you ahead in every game and creative project.
  • STUNNING 16 WQXGA 240 HZ DISPLAY - Ultra-smooth visuals with 100% DCI-P3 color accuracy and anti-glare tech for marathon sessions without eye strain.
  • BLAZING FAST INTEL CORE I 9 14900 HX - 24 cores, 32 threads, up to 5.8 GHz turbo for unstoppable multitasking and gaming power.
  • ULTIMATE CONNECTIVITY CUSTOMIZATION - Wi-Fi 6, Thunderbolt 4, RGB backlit keyboard, and a full suite of ports to keep you connected and in control.

The Lenovo Legion Pro is a powerhouse 16" gaming laptop featuring an Intel Core i9-14900HX processor with 24 cores and turbo speeds up to 5.8 GHz, paired with a top-tier NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4090 GPU. It boasts 64GB of ultra-fast DDR5 RAM and a massive 4TB PCIe NVMe SSD for seamless multitasking and storage. The vibrant 240Hz WQXGA display delivers stunning visuals with 100% DCI-P3 color accuracy and anti-glare technology. Equipped with Wi-Fi 6, Thunderbolt 4, and a customizable RGB backlit keyboard, this laptop is designed for professionals and gamers who demand peak performance and style.
